Ticket Booking System – Frontend Application

This frontend application provides a responsive, user-centric interface for browsing shows, viewing seat layouts, and booking seats in real time. It is developed with React and Vite and communicates securely with the backend API.

1. Overview

The frontend serves as the user-facing layer of the Ticket Booking System. It is designed for clarity, speed, and ease of interaction. Users can navigate through available shows, explore seat availability, select seats, and monitor the status of their bookings.

The application is tightly integrated with the backend through RESTful API calls, and it is deployed on Vercel for scalable, globally distributed access.

