The frontend relies on the following environment variable:

Variable	Description
VITE_API_URL	Public URL of the deployed backend

This value must be configured in Vercel during deployment.

6. Deployment

The frontend is deployed on Vercel, which provides automatic builds and global distribution.

Deployment steps:

Import the GitHub repository into Vercel.

Set the root directory to the frontend folder.

Configure the environment variable VITE_API_URL to point to the backend.

Allow Vercel to build and deploy the application.

Vercel generates a public frontend URL that users can access from any device.

